FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FSir Keir effectively fired the Foreign
OL,7,FOffice's top official Sir Olly Robbins
OL,8,Flast week after it emerged Lord
OL,9,FMandelson had been given developed
OL,10,Fvetting (DV) status despite failing
OL,11,Fchecks carried out by the agency
OL,12,Fresponsible for assessing security
OL,13,Fclearances.
OL,15,FWhitehall veteran Sir Olly is expected
OL,16,Fto give his own account to MPs on
OL,17,FTuesday at the Foreign Affairs
OL,18,FCommittee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FThe scandal has fuelled calls for Sir
OL,7,FKeir to resign, both from opposition
OL,8,Fparties but also from his critics
OL,9,Fwithin the Labour movement who already
OL,10,Ffear an electoral bloodbath for the
OL,11,Fparty in May's contests in English
OL,12,Fcouncils and the Scottish and Welsh
OL,13,Fparliaments.
OL,15,FThe Prime Minister's defence will be
OL,16,Fto blame officials for not telling him
OL,17,For the then foreign secretary David
OL,18,FLammy that UK Security Vetting (UKSV)
OL,19,Fhad not cleared Lord Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FA statement issued by No 10 on Sunday
OL,7,Fnight said that although civil
OL,8,Fservants rather than ministers make
OL,9,Fdecisions on vetting and clearance,
OL,10,Fthere was nothing in the law to
OL,11,Fprevent ministers being told.
OL,13,F"There is nothing in the guidance
OL,14,Fwhich prevented information being
OL,15,Fshared in this scenario, in a
OL,16,Fproportionate and necessary way and
OL,17,Fsubject to the appropriate procedural
OL,18,Fsteps," the statement on the
OL,19,FConstitutional Reform and Governance
OL,20,FAct said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
