PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FSir Keir told the Mirror he would make
OL,7,Fit "crystal clear" to MPs that he had
OL,8,Fbeen kept in the dark and it was
OL,9,F"unforgivable" that the Foreign Office
OL,10,Ffailed to tell him after he had
OL,11,Foffered public assurances that proper
OL,12,Fprocess had been followed.
OL,26,@oD@DOUoD@RO]qD@AOUqD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
