OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister said: "The fact
OL,7,Fthat I wasn't told that Peter
OL,8,FMandelson had failed his security
OL,9,Fvetting when he was appointed is
OL,10,Fastonishing. The fact that I wasn't
OL,11,Ftold when I said to Parliament that
OL,12,Fdue process had been followed is
OL,13,Funforgivable, and that's why I intend
OL,14,Fto set out in Parliament on Monday the
OL,15,Ffacts behind that, so there's full
OL,16,Ftransparency in relation to it.
OL,26,@nD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,F"But am I furious that I wasn't told?
OL,7,FYes, I am. Am I furious that other
OL,8,Fministers weren't told? Yes, I am. I
OL,9,Fshould have been told, and I wasn't
OL,10,Ftold."
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister will face
OL,13,Faccusations he misled Parliament `
OL,14,Fpotentially a resignation matter `
OL,15,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch has claimed
OL,16,FSir Keir is "either lying or he's
OL,17,Fincompetent".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@FO]xD@MOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
