CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FAsked if he would apologise to MPs on
OL,7,FMonday, the Prime Minister said: "I'm
OL,8,Fgoing to set out in terms what
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,F"But I shall be making it absolutely
OL,12,Fcrystal clear, as I have done a number
OL,13,Fof times, and I don't think anybody is
OL,14,Fdisputing this, that I was not told
OL,15,Fthat Peter Mandelson had failed his
OL,16,Fsecurity vetting, and I should have
OL,17,Fbeen told."
OL,19,FHe will say the information should
OL,20,Fhave been provided to both him and MPs
OL,21,Fa long time ago.
OL,26,@oD@bOUsD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FInstead, the Prime Minister was only
OL,7,Finformed about the vetting issue on
OL,8,FTuesday evening after the information
OL,9,Fwas uncovered as part of the process
OL,10,Fof gathering files related to Lord
OL,11,FMandelson's appointment to comply with
OL,12,Fan order by MPs to release all
OL,13,Frelevant documents.
OL,15,FAllies of the Prime Minister insisted
OL,16,Fthat Monday was the first opportunity
OL,17,Fhe has had to set out the full facts
OL,18,Fto Parliament, despite appearing in
OL,19,Fthe Commons on Wednesday for his
OL,20,Fregular question time session.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall told
OL,7,Fthe BBC: "I think one thing we've
OL,8,Flearned from this whole torrid episode
OL,9,Fis the need to get the facts
OL,10,Fabsolutely clear and right. That's
OL,11,Freally important."
OL,13,FIn a letter to the Prime Minister, Mrs
OL,14,FBadenoch said: "As an experienced
OL,15,Fbarrister you will know the importance
OL,16,Fof telling the truth, but you will
OL,17,Falso know that many people think you
OL,18,Fhave been at best recklessly negligent
OL,19,Fand at worst dishonest about this
OL,20,Fwhole affair.
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@RO]vD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer faces Commons showdown over
OL,4,CMandelson vetting scandal
OL,6,F"You have failed to answer very simple
OL,7,Fquestions about what you did and what
OL,8,Fyou knew. This is contemptuous of
OL,9,FParliament, discourteous to the House,
OL,10,Fand against the fundamental
OL,11,Frequirement set out in your own
OL,12,FMinisterial Code."
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was sacked last year,
OL,15,Fjust nine months into the Washington
OL,16,FDC posting, after further details of
OL,17,Fhis association with the paedophile
OL,18,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein emerged.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
